#!name=GitHub Downloader
#!desc=Download GitHub repository folder as ZIP archives
#!icon=https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/c0/ad/96/c0ad96cb-f93e-66c1-2ba4-facfca8c715e/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.png
